const user_id = pluginVariables[/* supabaseAuth user */ '1fa0dd68-5069-436c-9a7d-3b54c340f1fa']['user']?.['id']

const path = 'user_avatars/' + user_id;


const file_delete = path;

const { data, error } = await wwLib.wwPlugins.supabaseAuth.publicInstance
  .storage
  .from('system_images')
  .remove([file_delete])
  
  return file_delete
